                    </div>
                </div><div class="clear">
                </div>
                <div class="head-right" style="float: left; padding: 12px 0 0 10px; min-width:600px;">
                    <span class="ct-sort">设备号：<span id="txtSN" class="ct-detail"></span> </span><span
